{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"9da1cde6be","title":"介绍王国落人民公社","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"99da917071","index":0,"year":1959,"month":12,"day":2,"articleId":"9da1cde6be"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji42","name":"毛泽东全集第42卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/42-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji42":{"comments":[{"id":"384115a6ae","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9da1cde6be","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是为转发中共河北省委第一书记林铁关于王国落人民公社的情况报告写的批语，题目是毛泽东拟的。王国落，当时任河北省遵化县建明人民公社主任。"},{"id":"5cd34adb31","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9da1cde6be","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"林铁1959年11月26日给毛泽东的这一报告说，前几天我到王国落人民公社看了一下，发现这个社今年生产的结果是五业齐跃进，全面大丰收。这主要是因为他们依靠人民公社这个大集体的力量，鼓足了干劲，继承和发扬了勤俭办社的光荣传统，限苦奋斗，改善了生产条件。从去年以来，这个社还进行了大规模的水利建设，并积极开展了农业机械化、电气化建设。现在正在着手大搞社营经济，为进一步发展创造条件。"}],"contents":[{"id":"2e9d8e4947","type":"title","text":"介绍王国落人民公社！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9da1cde6be"},{"id":"384115a6ae","type":"paragraph","text":"此件发给各人民公社参考","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9da1cde6be"},{"id":"5cd34adb31","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9da1cde6be"},{"id":"0a365aeae6","type":"paragraph","text":"一九五九年十二月二日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9da1cde6be"}],"page":{"id":"b035fadf54","publicationId":"maoquanji42","articleId":"9da1cde6be","start":500,"end":500}}}},"__N_SSG":true}